v3.1 - one-tap Share/Print Quote, social banners, dark palette tuning

- Share/Print Quote: generates a branded quote PNG (IBI logo + price +
  breakdown) for the native share sheet on mobile; clean printable PDF on
  desktop (canvas-rendered, no libraries)
- Twitter/X header (1500x500) + OG link-preview banner (1200x630) generated
  from the brand mark; Open Graph + Twitter card meta added
- Dark theme retuned: deeper blue-tinted surfaces, brighter cyan, input glow
- Version bumped to v3.1; service-worker cache -> ibi-calc-v3.1.0

